Steam for Linux - launcher
==========================

This package contains a launching script that downloads and runs the Steam client program as the current user.

If you have just unpacked the archive, type "make install" to install,
or just run steam from the current directory.

Please visit http://www.steampowered.com/ for more information.

Enjoy!
 -- Valve Corporation

Reporting bugs
--------------

Issue tracking for Steam on Linux can be found here:
<https://github.com/ValveSoftware/steam-for-linux/>

The `subprojects/steam-devices` directory is maintained separately.
Please send bug reports, pull requests and suggestions to its Github
project: <https://github.com/ValveSoftware/steam-devices/>
